- **Android SDK** - Native Android app analytics via `/sdks/analytics/android/`
- **iOS SDK** - Native iOS app tracking through `/sdks/analytics/ios/`
- **React Native SDK** - Cross-platform mobile development support
- **Flutter SDK** - Google's UI toolkit integration
- **Unity SDK** - Game development platform support
- **Unreal SDK** - Game engine integration
- **Node.js SDK** - Server-side JavaScript tracking
- **Python SDK** - Server-side Python implementation
